  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Learn French, German, Italian, Lithuanian, Polish, Portuguese, Spanish, Japanese, Chinese & Korean like a polyglot! This quiz game helps you review words like a proper polyglot. Over 10,000 words spread across 10 languages for all your learning efforts. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > All questions have a timer set between 2 and 20 seconds.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Choose how many questions per quiz. From 3 to 30.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Check the number of languages in the list below </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > You can review any language vocabulary.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > The questions can be either in English or in the target language</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build vocabulary in the following languages:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >        French</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >        German</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >        Italian</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >        Lithuanian</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >        Polish</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >        Portuguese</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >        Spanish</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >        Japanese</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >        Chinese</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >        Korean</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Learn French, German, Italian, Lithuanian, Polish, Portuguese, Spanish, Japanese, Chinese & Korean like a polyglot! This quiz game helps you review words like a proper polyglot. Over 10,000 words spread across 10 languages for all your learning efforts. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > All questions have a timer set between 2 and 20 seconds.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Choose how many questions per quiz. From 3 to 30.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Check the number of languages in the list below </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > You can review any language vocabulary.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > The questions can be either in English or in the target language</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build vocabulary in the following languages:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >        French</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >        German</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >        Italian</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >        Lithuanian</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >        Polish</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >        Portuguese</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >        Spanish</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >        Japanese</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >        Chinese</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >        Korean</p>",
